@startuml
title 个性化偏好与设备别名参与执行顺序图（简化视图）
actor "家庭用户" as User
participant "Frontend Views\nPersonalizationCard / DevicesView / VoiceControlView" as FE
participant "Frontend API\npersonalization.js / command.js" as API
participant "Backend Router\nuser router / commands router" as Router
participant "CommandExecutor" as Exec
participant "personalization service" as PersonalService
participant "Text Understanding Pipeline" as Pipeline
database "SQLite\nuser_preferences / device_aliases / command_logs" as DB

== 偏好维护 ==
User -> FE: 保存默认方言或输入方式
FE -> API: PATCH /api/user/preferences
API -> Router: preferred_dialect / preferred_input_mode
Router -> DB: get_or_create then update user_preferences
DB --> Router: updated preference
Router --> API: success envelope
API --> FE: show saved

== 设备别名维护 ==
User -> FE: 新建设备别名
FE -> API: POST /api/user/device-aliases
API -> Router: device_id + alias
Router -> DB: check current-user alias uniqueness
Router -> DB: insert device_aliases
DB --> Router: alias detail
Router --> API: success envelope
API --> FE: refresh aliases

== 个性化参与指令执行 ==
User -> FE: 执行“打开小灯”
FE -> API: POST /api/commands/execute
API -> Router: command text
Router -> Exec: execute(command, context)
Exec -> PersonalService: get preferences and match alias
PersonalService -> DB: read preference and aliases
DB --> PersonalService: preferred_dialect + alias_match
PersonalService --> Exec: personalization context
Exec -> Pipeline: rewrite alias, correct, normalize, parse
Pipeline --> Exec: ParseResult with alias_match and Parser confidence
Exec -> DB: write preference_used and alias_match
Exec --> Router: execution result
Router --> API: success/code/message/data
API --> FE: show result
@enduml
